1324
00:39:47.852 --> 00:39:53.656  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:55.71%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>be needing this anymore.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1325
00:40:05.225 --> 00:40:07.006  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:53.81%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>(</c.mono_sans></c.white><i><c.white><c.mono_sans> sighing contentedly )</c.mono_sans></c.white></i>

