1328
00:40:31.079 --> 00:40:31.559  position:40.48%,start  align:start size:27.14%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Just you?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1329
00:40:32.121 --> 00:40:33.482  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:50.00%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I dropped my crew off</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1330
00:40:33.482 --> 00:40:34.553  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:42.38%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>at a Maquis base.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1331
00:40:35.955 --> 00:40:38.276  position:30.95%,start  align:start size:46.19%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I</c.mono_sans></c.white><i><c.white><c.mono_sans> had</c.mono_sans></c.white></i><c.white><c.mono_sans> to come back,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

