1335
00:40:41.710 --> 00:40:43.211  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:38.57%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>You didn't have</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1336
00:40:41.710 --> 00:40:43.211  position:30.95%,start  align:start size:48.10%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>to come back either.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1337
00:40:44.109 --> 00:40:47.628  position:38.57%,start  align:start size:30.95%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Yes. I did.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1338
00:40:48.089 --> 00:40:49.310  position:27.14%,start  align:start size:55.71%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>And I think we both know</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1339
00:40:49.310 --> 00:40:51.342  position:29.05%,start  align:start size:51.90%  line:79.29% 
