<c.white><c.mono_sans>You had your duty.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1345
00:41:03.673 --> 00:41:05.673  position:38.57%,start  align:start size:30.95%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I had mine.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1346
00:41:06.074 --> 00:41:07.435  position:29.05%,start  align:start size:50.00%  line:84.62% 
