1347
00:41:09.553 --> 00:41:11.753  position:42.38%,start  align:start size:23.33%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I know.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1348
00:41:11.753 --> 00:41:14.991  position:40.48%,start  align:start size:29.05%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>And I know</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1349
00:41:11.753 --> 00:41:14.991  position:23.33%,start  align:start size:61.43%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I'll probably go to prison.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1350
00:41:17.093 --> 00:41:20.115  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:67.14%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>But I came back because of us.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1351
00:41:21.237 --> 00:41:23.258  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:38.57%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Because despite</c.mono_sans></c.white>

