1355
00:41:32.797 --> 00:41:34.037  position:42.38%,start  align:start size:23.33%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Do you?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1356
00:41:37.160 --> 00:41:38.156  position:46.19%,start  align:start size:15.71%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>No.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

